    {
      "id": "Q4qUPIAIsHVTbpR1Pbn8A",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 480.2639465332031,
      "y": 1534.1844482421875,
      "width": 863.0393676757812,
      "height": 1175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ah",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2002426545,
      "version": 1461,
      "versionNonce": 1356594111,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781340849046,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Types:\n1. In memory cache : \n2. Distributed cache : Redis\n\nCaching strategies:\na. Reads\n    - Cache aside : \n        Cache hit : read from cache\n        Cache miss : Service reads from DB and stores in cache\n\n\n \n    \n- Cache through :\n        Cache hit : read from cache\n        cache miss : Service reads from Cache and cache reads from DB, persists in cache\n\n\n\nb. Writes\n    - Write through : \n        Service writes to cache and cache writes to DB\n\n\n\n\n    - Write Around :\n        Service writes to DB and when read from cache, cache reads from DB and writes\n\n\n   \n    \n    - Write Back :\n        Service writes to cache, cache async flushes to DB    \n\n\n\n\n\n\nBenefits\n- Performance\n- Fault tolerance\n- Ability to scale cache\n\nCache Eviction strategies\n- FIFO, LFU, LRU",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Types:\n1. In memory cache : \n2. Distributed cache : Redis\n\nCaching strategies:\na. Reads\n    - Cache aside : \n        Cache hit : read from cache\n        Cache miss : Service reads from DB and stores in cache\n\n\n \n    \n- Cache through :\n        Cache hit : read from cache\n        cache miss : Service reads from Cache and cache reads from DB, persists in cache\n\n\n\nb. Writes\n    - Write through : \n        Service writes to cache and cache writes to DB\n\n\n\n\n    - Write Around :\n        Service writes to DB and when read from cache, cache reads from DB and writes\n\n\n   \n    \n    - Write Back :\n        Service writes to cache, cache async flushes to DB    \n\n\n\n\n\n\nBenefits\n- Performance\n- Fault tolerance\n- Ability to scale cache\n\nCache Eviction strategies\n- FIFO, LFU, LRU",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
