      "updated": 1781341286839,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Durable component that Supports Async communication\n- Ex : Kafka\n- Decouples communication between services\n\nBenefits : \n- Producers can produce anytime, consumer can consume anytime\n- P and C can be scaled independently\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Durable component that Supports Async communication\n- Ex : Kafka\n- Decouples communication between services\n\nBenefits : \n- Producers can produce anytime, consumer can consume anytime\n- P and C can be scaled independently\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
