      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Uses REST over HTTP for communication\n- Idempotency\n\nResponse code\n200 : OK\n201 : Created\n202 : Accepted\n\n400 : Bad request\n401 : Unauthorized\n403 : Forbidden\n404 : Not found\n429 : too many request\n\n500 : internal server error\n501 : Not implemented\n502 : bad gateway\n503 : Service unavailable\n504 : Gateway timeout",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Uses REST over HTTP for communication\n- Idempotency\n\nResponse code\n200 : OK\n201 : Created\n202 : Accepted\n\n400 : Bad request\n401 : Unauthorized\n403 : Forbidden\n404 : Not found\n429 : too many request\n\n500 : internal server error\n501 : Not implemented\n502 : bad gateway\n503 : Service unavailable\n504 : Gateway timeout",
