      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Other concepts\n\n1. Logging\n2. Metrics and SLOs\n    a. Host level metrics : CPU, memory etc\n    b. Aggregate level : Performance of DB, cache\n    c. Business metrics : DAU, retention, revenue\n3. Automation :\n    a. Continious delivery\n    b. Continious integration",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Other concepts\n\n1. Logging\n2. Metrics and SLOs\n    a. Host level metrics : CPU, memory etc\n    b. Aggregate level : Performance of DB, cache\n    c. Business metrics : DAU, retention, revenue\n3. Automation :\n    a. Continious delivery\n    b. Continious integration",
